# eng.case planned package surface
#
# Purpose:
#   per-case manifests for sample-to-run workflows.
#
# Current implementation:
#   no native case manifest module yet. Workflow examples use explicit sample
#   tables, generated files, process results, and output manifests.
#
# Planned CaseManifest fields:
#   case_id
#   sample row hash
#   case directory
#   generated input files
#   process command and status
#   result files
#   metrics
#   failure reason
